ressive for a fungus.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\UND_SporeServant_RD.html", "a7271be6-d316-1f63-7f10-d6ffd3d9f4b7"], "h0253fbc8g964dg4c94gb1e8g35e7f7289e93": ["| I disagree. I want option A (ShadowHeart Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\UND_SporeServant_RD.html", "a7271be6-d316-1f63-7f10-d6ffd3d9f4b7"], "hda73246dgf267g4066g9e03g8d1a960f3b69": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\UND_SporeServant_RD.html", "a7271be6-d316-1f63-7f10-d6ffd3d9f4b7"], "hfa7e93fcga457g4ab1g9371gdb6b23d5182c": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\UND_SporeServant_RD.html", "a7271be6-d316-1f63-7f10-d6ffd3d9f4b7"], "h83204c1cg5e6eg4297g9ad4g342a2db5c792": ["| I disagree. I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\UND_SporeServant_RD.html", "a7271be6-d316-1f63-7f10-d6ffd3d9f4b7"], "h42226b2ag2b4cg44fcg8f23g2ee66da48c5b": ["| I disagree. I want option A (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\UND_SporeServant_RD.html", "a7271be6-d316-1f63-7f10-d6ffd3d9f4b7"], "h66ed9f1cg32f5g434agbecagd3df735ea44c": ["Well, I'd like a cadre of servants following me around. Sounds nice.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\UND_SporeServant_RD.html", "a7271be6-d316-1f63-7f10-d6ffd3d9f4b7"], "h6d8fddfbg69cag425fg8a67g061a106fff12": ["Forget necromancy indeed. I prefer steel and fire.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\UND_SporeServant_RD.html", "5800ce6a-a962-bef1-ecd9-86c38feb7fa7"], "h17cd566agd11eg47d2gb777g64e5b80b9526": ["A waste of time, besides. You crave power? Become an army unto yourself.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", "